title: Did the Queen ‘Reveal’ an ‘Upsetting Truth About Archie’?
subtitle: A clickbait advertisement led to an 80-page story about Queen Elizabeth II and Archie, the son of Prince Harry and Meghan Markle.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: Queen Elizabeth II revealed an upsetting truth about Archie, the son of Prince Harry and Meghan Markle.
